textContent:
---best bday---

Halu bby! I just want to tell you how lucky and happy I felt furing my bday! This is legitimately the best birthday I've had in years and it's all because of you! You've made my life a thousand times better and you're my best gift. I promised God that I'll cherish you forever and ever.

I'm also very very very lucky with your family. I'm so happy with their gifts and everything else. Apaka bait and sweet and thoughtful nilang lahat and I'm so so so lucky to be a part of their family too! 

I love you my bby!! Thank you! For your gifts, for your efforts, for the cake, for the video, for the poem, and for everything else!!! MWAA YOU REALLY MAKE EVERYTHING BETTER HUHUHU
